name: 壁尻并带有头像 | stuck in wall with a profile photo
description:
Stuck your favorite character into wall, with this LoRA.

Training is based on AbyssOrangeMix3 model.

In the belowing image, first column is with no LoRA, second is with 0.8 weight, third is with 1 weight. Through rows, there's comparison amoung concepts and character sittings. | 下图中第一列是不用LoAR、第二列是0.8 LoRA权重，第三列1权重。每行每行是不同的概念，比如卡墙里上半身视角、下半身视角、以及带有照片的。

You can customize the character with prompts together with "stuck in wall, multiple views, lower body with profile". 卡墙里带有照片的可以用prompt控制照片上的人物。

Notice that "lower body with profile" often show no face photo if you doesn't define the character's facial feature with prompt. Should add "XXX hair, XXX eyes" to prompt. 注意，如果不描述一下角色的面部，通常不会带有头像照片。

modelVersions.description:
Trigger Words for concept「lower body with a profile photo」:

stuck in wall, lower body with profile, multiple views, kneepits

Resolution may influence image composition, I recommend use 512x1024 for this concept, otherwise image maybe not long enough to contain both the lower body and profile photo.

Trigger Words for concept 「upper body only」:

stuck in wall, upper body only, hanging breasts
